snippet.title: Tu Hai | Official Music Video | Darshan Raval | Neha Sharma | Prakriti Giri | Gurpreet Saini
snippet.description:
#TuHai #DarshanRaval #NehaSharma #PrakritiGiri #Dubai #NewSong2024 #IndieMusicLabel

Whether you're lounging on a sunny day or stargazing under the night sky, "Tu Hai" is the perfect soundtrack to accompany those moments of love and connection. This enchanting song, brought to life by the melodious voices of Darshan Raval and Prakriti Giri, captures the essence of romance like never before. With the captivating beauty of Neha Sharma and heartfelt lyrics penned by Gurpreet Saini, "Tu Hai" is guaranteed to make your heart flutter. Join us on a journey of love and passion as we serenade you with this soul-stirring composition.

snippet.title: A Day at TV Serial Set üì∫ | Take A Break
snippet.description:
Get ready for a hilarious peek behind the scenes in our newest comedy sketch, "A Day at the TV Serial Set"! üé¨ü§£
Join us as we take you on a wild ride through the chaotic world of Indian television serials, where melodrama reigns supreme and the antics behind the camera are just as entertaining as the stories unfolding on screen.
In this laugh-out-loud sketch, we introduce you to a motley crew of characters that populate the set of a typical TV serial. From the overzealous director with a penchant for dramatic gestures to the perpetually stressed-out production assistant juggling a million tasks at once, each member of the crew adds their own unique flavor to the comedy mix.

Join us as we take you on a wild ride through the chaotic world of Indian television serials, where melodrama reigns supreme and the antics behind the camera are just as entertaining as the stories unfolding on screen.
In this laugh-out-loud sketch, we introduce you to a motley crew of characters that populate the set of a typical TV serial. From the overzealous director with a penchant for dramatic gestures to the perpetually stressed-out production assistant juggling a million tasks at once, each member of the crew adds their own unique flavor to the comedy mix.

snippet.description:
Amazon miniTV presents 
Chacha Vidhayak Hain Humare Season 3 2024 

Dil thaam ke baithiye kyuki Chacha Vidhayak Hai Humare ka season 3 aa raha hai.

Starring: Zakir Khan, Abhimanyu Singh, Amruta Khanvilkar, Zakir Hussain, Alka Amin, Kumar Varun, Vyom Sharma, Venus
Directed By: Gaganjeet Singh
Casting: Shivam Gupta
Written By: Zakir Khan, Gopal Dutt, Shubham Dubey, Sahil Verma, Badri Chavan, Bharath Chavan, Niketan Sharma
Show Runner & Executive Producer - Alia Curmally
Produced By: Sakht Films & OML Entertainment Pvt.ltd

About The Show
Rohit Pathak aka Ronny started out a young lad whose life is not driven by big ambitions. All he wanted was a comfortable life where he could boast about himself using convenient lies. He pretends to be the nephew of currently-serving regional politician the much-feared charismatic Ashwini Pathak (the MLA), since they both share the same last name. His friends and followers take his word for the ultimate truth, and it‚Äôs all great fun until ‚Äòuncle‚Äô and ‚Äònephew‚Äô come face to face.

snippet.title: Manipur Election 2024: Voting in Manipur Marred by Irregularities and Tensions
snippet.description:
Manipur Election 2024: Voting in Manipur is underway amidst tensions and allegations of irregularities in the Inner Manipur constituency. Polling was halted at two locations, Uripok in Imphal West and Thongju in Imphal East, after EVMs were destroyed, prompting the polling officer to close the booths. Additionally, voting was stopped.

Shiddat Digitally Presented by PEL

Asra, a beautiful and cherished young woman, has led a life filled with love and care from her family. In contrast, Sultan, a determined and charismatic perfectionist, overcomes the challenges of his troubled childhood to consistently achieve his desires.

Despite their stark personality differences, Asra falls in love with Sultan. However, after they marry, Asra realizes that Sultan is not the ideal man she had envisioned. To please him, she sacrifices her desires and undergoes a significant transformation.

This revelation becomes the catalyst for an unending series of problems between them. The journey through marital life becomes a complex maze as Asra and Sultan attempt to navigate challenges, each trying to mold the other according to their own will and preference.

Will Asra and Sultan change for each other, or will the growing list of problems between them persist? When Asra discovers the reality about Sultan, how will she react? Is Sultan contemplating leaving Asra? Can love overcome all obstacles, or are some differences too profound to bridge?

snippet.title: EATING out & SHOPPING with Parents | Mom's Homemade REMEDIES for bloating
snippet.description:
Mom's Homemade REMEDIES for bloating | EATING out & SHOPPING 

Our families have been following the Ayurvedic way for after-birth treatments and it includes herbs and spices from our garden or surroundings. And we have been following it still and will be passing it on to the next generations. 
One of the best remedies for bloating is a mix of some ingredients I have included in the video which is a bit spicy and for balancing we add palm jaggery. The measurments for each ingredient is not exact. its taken with no proper measuring cups or any. However, the amount needs to be adjusted accordingly.

----------------------------------
Online purchase links

a. IRON vessels

Iron Skillet - https://amzn.to/3Hfrj57

- 3 ltr - https://amzn.to/3XkS4uQ
- 5 ltr - https://amzn.to/3GTeE6y
- 7.5 ltr - https://amzn.to/3ITTubg

c. Stainless Steel Pressure cooker Clip-on -
5 ltr - https://amzn.to/3WnkXFd

f. Puttu maker -
- With bowl - https://amzn.to/3JvSV7Z
- Cooker top - https://amzn.to/3XDcdMz
- Cheratta puttu - https://amzn.to/3kFtruq

g. Idiyappam maker - https://amzn.to/3Hu89sn

h. Steamer Stainless Steel -
- 2 ltr - https://amzn.to/3R4YUlK
- Insert - https://amzn.to/3Ww1O44
- 3 tier - https://amzn.to/3Xzw4fV

i. Kids Tiffin box - 
  a. https://amzn.to/40ySpfb
  b. https://amzn.to/3YdCnH5

j. Ikea chopping board - https://amzn.to/3Y9WUup

O. DISH organizer above sink- https://amzn.to/43HP8Ly
===============================

Bloating medicine :

Long pepper - a handful , https://amzn.to/4d8bkDZ
Dry ginger - a handful, https://amzn.to/4d6TnWo
Black pepper - a handful , https://amzn.to/4aL997G
These ingredients should be half the amount of the next ingredients as these are spicy in flavour

Dill seeds - 2 handful , https://amzn.to/448EIpv
Carom seeds - 2 handful , https://amzn.to/44bKneo

Palm Jaggery - melt and add according to the taste needed., https://amzn.to/3w1TQbF

--------------
Ginger Coffee & other winter home remedies - https://youtu.be/ycVY-te0QTM

-----------------

Green coconut chutney -

Grated coconut - 2 cups
warm water - 1/2 cup or more if needed
curd - 1 cup
green chillies - 4 - 5
ginger - a small piece
shallots - 4
coriander leaves - a ahndful
salt

mustard seeds - 1 tsp
curry leaves - few
dried red chillies - 2 - 3

Asra, a beautiful and cherished young woman, has led a life filled with love and care from her family. In contrast, Sultan, a determined and charismatic perfectionist, overcomes the challenges of his troubled childhood to consistently achieve his desires.

Despite their stark personality differences, Asra falls in love with Sultan. However, after they marry, Asra realizes that Sultan is not the ideal man she had envisioned. To please him, she sacrifices her desires and undergoes a significant transformation.

Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Shiddat Episode 24 Teaser - 22nd April 2024 - Har Pal Geo

Asra, a beautiful and cherished young woman, has led a life filled with love and care from her family. In contrast, Sultan, a determined and charismatic perfectionist, overcomes the challenges of his troubled childhood to consistently achieve his desires.

Despite their stark personality differences, Asra falls in love with Sultan. However, after they marry, Asra realizes that Sultan is not the ideal man she had envisioned. To please him, she sacrifices her desires and undergoes a significant transformation.

This revelation becomes the catalyst for an unending series of problems between them. The journey through marital life becomes a complex maze as Asra and Sultan attempt to navigate challenges, each trying to mold the other according to their own will and preference.

Will Asra and Sultan change for each other, or will the growing list of problems between them persist? When Asra discovers the reality about Sultan, how will she react? Is Sultan contemplating leaving Asra? Can love overcome all obstacles, or are some differences too profound to bridge?

7th Sky Entertainment Presentation
Producers: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi
Director: Zeeshan Ahmed
Writer: Zanjabeel Asim


Cast:
Muneeb Butt as Sultan 
Anmol Baloch as Asra
Noor ul Hassan as Abdul Mannan 
Erum Akhtar as Talat

Ismat Zaidi as Sarwat
Namra Shahid as Mishal
Fajjer Khan as Hala
Zain Afzal as Junaid
Sami Khan as Shayan
Sohail Masood as Mansoor

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta', is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' and a mischievous son 'Tapu'. Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalal' to call his father 'Champaklal' from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

snippet.title: Ye Kannu Kuttindho Yamunike | HanuMan | Teja Sajja, Varalakshmi, Kala Bhairava | Telugu New Songs
snippet.description:
Embark on an emotional journey with 'Ye Kannu Kuttindho Yamunike' from the Telugu movie Hanuman. This soul-stirring song, sung by Kala Bhairava, beautifully captures the bond of love between siblings. Let the heartfelt lyrics and melodious tunes resonate with your emotions. Directed By Prasanth Varma, Music By Krishna Saurabh Surampalli, Lyrics Penned By Krishna Kanth

Stay updated with the latest videos from Tips Telugu, Subscribe on the below link
https://youtube.com/TipsTelugu

Song Details : 
Music Composer: Krishna Saurabh Surampalli
Lyrics: Krishna Kanth
Singer: Kala Bhairava
Alap Vocals: Yadu Krishnan 
Additional Vocals: Yadu Krishnan, Prateek Nag


Movie Details : 
Written and directed by Prasanth Varma
Starring Teja Sajja, Amritha Aiyer, Varalakshmi Sarath Kumar, Vinay Rai, Raj Deepak Shetty, Vennela Kishore, Getup Srinu, Satya etc.,
Produced by K. Niranjan Reddy

Lyrics: 
Ye Kannu Kuttindho Yamunike 
Ye Manta Puttindo Shivunike
Manchollu Kindhunte Thagadhane 
Muncharaa Kanneeti Varadhane

Ammai Nuvvu Penchavuga Akkanu 
Sthanam Minchavuga Akharidhaka 
Andundhira Nanne Kaachi Usurodhilera

Yem Seyyalo Theliyadhe 
Anthe Leni Baruvidhe

Ni Pelli Mantralu Nilichena
Na Gunde Vekkekki Yedchena 
Panneeru Jalleti Velana 
Kanneeru Makinka Migilena

Sinna Naatane Uppumootala 
Etthukunna Nuvve Neti Dhakanu 
Viduvaledhule Pattukunna Cheyye

Kammenemo Cheekatle 
Poddugalane Panamleni 
Ni Kalle Soose Yelane
 
Mandalinche Ni Gonthe 
Chinna Boyene Nuvve Leni 
Ee Inta Yetta Undane

Ye Kannu Kuttindo Y
amunike Ye Manta 
Puttindo Shivunike
Manchollu Kindhunte 
Thagadhane Munchara 
Kanneeti Varadhane

Ammay Nuvvu Penchavuga 
Akkanu Sthanam Minchavuga 
Akharidhaka Andundhira 
Nanne Kaachi Usurodhilera
Kaalipoye Bathukule 
Boodidhayye Guruthule

snippet.description:
Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Khumar Episode 46 [Eng Sub] Digitally Presented by Happilac Paints - Feroze Khan - Neelam Muneer - 20th April 2024 - Har Pal Geo

Khumar Digitally Presented by Happilac Paints

Khumar is a timeless love story that delves into the challenges arising from societal class differences and the negativity that stems from them. Khumar explores the complexities of love in the face of societal expectations and challenges. Faiz and Hareem, two individuals from different backgrounds, find their lives connected by destiny.

Faiz, born into an affluent family, contrasts sharply with Hareem, who hails from a
lower-middle-class background. Despite their differences, fate weaves their paths together. Hareem, diligently working to make ends meet amid her brother Rufi's educational needs and her mother's medical expenses, faces numerous hurdles. In the midst of her struggles, Faiz, a friend of Rufi's, silently supports them financially and even gets work for Hareem, albeit discreetly.

Hareem's family doesn't know that Faiz loves her, leading to a one-sided love affair. Faiz's love for Hareem remains a secret, but his mother disapproves of his association with Hareem's family due to the significant class difference. But fate decides to play its tune, and an unexpected event turns the lives of Faiz and Hareem upside down.

What was this surprising turn of events that changed everything for Faiz and Hareem? Will the gap in their social status keep them apart? Can Faiz convince his mother to accept Hareem? If they marry, can they create a happy life together despite their different backgrounds and mindsets?

7th Sky Entertainment Presentation 
Producers: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi 
Writer: Maha Malik
Director: Ali Faizan

Cast:
Feroze Khan as Faiz
Neelam Muneer as Hareem
Hina Bayat as Kehkasha Begum
Asma Abbas as Durdana
Behroz Sabzwari as Sheikh Furqan
Zainab Qayoom as Dil Araa
Shehryar Zaidi as Taufeeq
Adnan Samad as Nasir
Sheherzade Peerzada as Hamna  
Minsa Malik as Laiba 
Kinza Malik as Atiya
Mehmood Akhtar as Zaawar  
Agha Mustafa as Rayyan  
Hamzah Tariq as Rufi
Ayesha Rajpoot as Shagufta
Mizna Waqas as Husna
Sohail Masood as Mirza Sahab
Birjees Farooqui as Salma

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in 'Gokuldham Co-operative Society' and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. The show predominantly - promotes 'Jethalaal' (Dilip Joshi), a Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta' (Shailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Nitish Bhaluni). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises.
